description:
In just four years after starting her video blog, Jerry Heil became a breakthrough artist in Ukraine's music industry, already having a music label to her name. Each of her songs has become an internet sensation, amassing over 175.5 million views on her official YouTube channel in the last year alone, making her one of Ukraine's most famous singers and songwriters. Jerry Heil represented Ukraine at Eurovision 2024 alongside rapper alyona alyona, performing the song "Teresa & Maria" and securing the honorable 3rd place in the contest's grand final. 

She is one of the few Ukrainians who managed to enter Berklee College of Music, one of the most prestigious music universities in the world. Jerry Heil believes that her musical mission is to glorify Ukrainian traditions and culture around the globe.
